{"tid":1791824,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"屍體發現紀錄","createTime":"2019-12-21T07:13:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T07:55:16.000Z","uid":51143,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ef4c4c505772414ff463370e9b851b9ed21543b5","tid":1791824,"uid":51143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:13:18.000Z","msg":"嘗試緊整理近來發生既屍體發現紀錄，希望其他有心人可以有用，但發現資料好難揾。<br />\n<br />\n1) 政府唔公佈每一單CASE。<br />\n2) 新聞媒體未能每一單都報導，有啲CASE係LIHKG或者IG/FACEBOOK先見到。<br />\n3) 大部份CASE知道發生左就完，冇資料再跟進，例如驗屍後既死因。<br />\n<br />\n諗住用Google Form去做紀錄。<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfzBFarajggTAjdCKjkx9J0JERR0Qt4CkN9Y7dd4_egd633lw/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSfzBFarajggTAjdCKjkx9J0JERR0Qt4CkN9Y7dd4_egd633lw%2Fviewform&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=473ca8c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSfzBFarajggTAjdCKjkx9J0JERR0Qt4CkN9Y7dd4_egd633lw/viewform</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1etIzJiN5dOfKMEh34uWBT_CHqQE25hFdEfTpV87OqU8/edit#gid=1360711683\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1etIzJiN5dOfKMEh34uWBT_CHqQE25hFdEfTpV87OqU8%2Fedit%23gid%3D1360711683&d=Wr%2FXdV%2FekiVpClOitW4NQRZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=e6fa0101\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1etIzJiN5dOfKMEh34uWBT_CHqQE25hFdEfTpV87OqU8/edit#gid=1360711683</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇人有啲頭緒可以點做落去？"},{"pid":"969f8f7fb42a77b4b5fc6751ef3edcb0525cb5a3","tid":1791824,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"可以入返之前個啲嗎"},{"pid":"5710834b54733da47d867b13de59abbf757f8011","tid":1791824,"uid":51143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969f8f7fb42a77b4b5fc6751ef3edcb0525cb5a3","tid":1791824,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T07:23:24.000Z","msg":"可以入